e; tng trong vic truyn ti tinh thn ca nm K Hi &ndash; m&agrave; n&oacute; li nm  mt c&acirc;u chuyn to ln hn m&agrave; Dosiin s nhc n sau &acirc;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vi tp tc ca ngi phng &ocirc;ng, cng ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; vn ho&aacute; ca ch&uacute;ng ta th&igrave; t&ecirc;n gi ca nhng ch&ograve;m sao quen thuc nh Bo B&igrave;nh, Thi&ecirc;n B&igrave;nh, Bach Dng,&hellip; hay tng hp li c&ograve;n gi l&agrave; Cung Ho&agrave;ng o li kh&ocirc;ng phi h thng t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n c trng. M&agrave; Can Chi, vn tt li t cm ch Thp Can Thp Nh Chi mi l&agrave; h thng &aacute;nh s th&agrave;nh chu k&igrave; c s dng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"501\" src=\"https://dosi-in.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Horoscopo_Chino_u_Horoscopo_Occidental_%C2%BFCua%CC%81l_eliges-.jpg\" width=\"1003\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo Wikipedia, Can Chi c &aacute;p dng vi t hp chu k&igrave; s&aacute;u mi trong &acirc;m lch n&oacute;i chung  x&aacute;c nh t&ecirc;n gi ca thi gian. C&ograve;n trong i sng, ch&uacute;ng ta bit ti n gin hn l&agrave; 12 con Gi&aacute;p khi u t: T&iacute; (Chut) &ndash; Su (Tr&acirc;u) &ndash; Dn (H) &ndash; M&atilde;o/Mo (M&egrave;o/Th) &ndash; Th&igrave;n (Rng) &ndash; T (Rn) &ndash; Ng (Nga) &ndash; M&ugrave;i (D&ecirc;/Cu) &ndash; Th&acirc;n (Kh) &ndash; Du (G&agrave;) &ndash; Tut (Ch&oacute;) &ndash; Hi (Heo). Nm 2019 n&agrave;y, hay theo s ph&acirc;n chia ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; nm K Hi, ng thi cng ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; con vt kt th&uacute;c cho 1 gi&aacute;p ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; &yacute; ngha ch&iacute;nh cho to&agrave;n b c&aacute;c thit k n t BST n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kh&ocirc;ng nh nhng ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh trc &acirc;y, m&agrave; Nike ng dng phong c&aacute;ch &ldquo;What The&rdquo; quen thuc cc ni ting ca m&igrave;nh v&agrave;o trong c&aacute;c thit k gii hn ln n&agrave;y. To&agrave;n b nhng ho tit &atilde; tng xut hin  c&aacute;c nm trc u hin din tr li, nhng ch di 1 phi&ecirc;n bn duy nht ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; Air Max