cute;c vi bt k d&ograve;ng n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n t giy. Bn c&oacute; th ng, ngi tr&ecirc;n gh hoc c&uacute;i xung.<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://bountysneakers.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/tim_size_giay_2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. V ph&aacute;c tho b&agrave;n ch&acirc;n ca bn bng 1 ng lin xung quanh. Bn c&oacute; th mang v m&agrave; bn d nh mc vi &ocirc;i gi&agrave;y mun mua, nhng kh&ocirc;ng mang gi&agrave;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. &aacute;nh du chiu d&agrave;i v&agrave; chiu rng ca b&agrave;n ch&acirc;n tr&ecirc;n giy. S dng im &aacute;nh du  v ng thng chm v&agrave;o mi b&ecirc;n ca ng vin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. o chiu d&agrave;i b&agrave;n ch&acirc;n. S dng thc o bng hoc thc k  o t tr&ecirc;n xung di. Vit, ghi nh con s n&agrave;y, n&oacute; s quyt nh phn ln c gi&agrave;y ca bn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. o chiu rng ca b&agrave;n ch&acirc;n. o gia c&aacute;c ng  b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i v&agrave; b&ecirc;n phi v&agrave; lu s xung. Nhiu &ocirc;i gi&agrave;y c&oacute; chiu rng kh&aacute;c nhau, v&igrave; vy con s n&agrave;y s quyt nh phi&ecirc;n bn n&agrave;o cn mua.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. Tr khong 0.5 cm t mi s. iu n&agrave;y l&agrave;  ph&ugrave; hp vi kh&ocirc;ng gian nh gia c&aacute;c d&ograve;ng c thc hin bi b&uacute;t ch&igrave; v&agrave; ch&acirc;n thc t ca bn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://bountysneakers.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/tim_size_giay_7.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. S dng s o chiu d&agrave;i v&agrave; chiu rng  t&igrave;m k&iacute;ch thc gi&agrave;y ca bn tr&ecirc;n biu  k&iacute;ch thc. Nam v&agrave; n s dng c&aacute;c k&iacute;ch c kh&aacute;c nhau, cng nh c&aacute;c quc gia kh&aacute;c nhau.<br />\r\n<b>c bit lu &yacute;: size n US s kh&aacute;c vi size nam US, v&agrave; size Adidas US s kh&aacute;c size Nike US.</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. Sm mt &ocirc;i&nbsp;<a href=\"https://bountysneakers.com/danh-muc/adidas/\">gi&agrave;y Adidas</a>, gi&agrave;y Nike ti ca h&agrave;ng&nbsp;<a href=\"http://giayadidas.com.vn/\">Adidas Vit Nam</a>, Nike Vit Nam ngay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://bountysneakers.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/tim_size_giay_8.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n','2019-06-19 15:28:42','2019-06-20 17:08:08',1,2),(5,'<h1><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/14-11.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px; height: 461px;\" />Top 5 Phng Ph&aacute;p Ph&acirc;n Bit Gi&agrave;y Nike N Real Cho C&aacute;c T&iacute;n  Nike</h1>\r\n','<p>Bn l&agrave; t&iacute;n  gi&agrave;y Nike n m&agrave; vn cha d&aacute;m mua v&igrave; c&ograve;n lo s &ldquo;rinh&rdquo; phi  gi? Bn cc k y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch khi thy c&aacute;c shop gi&agrave;y nike ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng qung c&aacute;o nhng mu m&atilde; mi nhng li s &oacute; l&agrave; h&agrave;ng FAKE.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"giy Nike n\" data-lazy-src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/14-11.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"461\" src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/14-11.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>H&igrave;nh nh:&nbsp;gi&agrave;y Nike n</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>1. Nhn bit qua Tem gi&agrave;y Nike n</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Ging vi c&aacute;c sn phm kh&aacute;c, i vi Gi&agrave;y Nike sau khi th&agrave;nh phm xut ra th trng ti&ecirc;u th. Mi &ocirc;i gi&agrave;y iu c gn cho m&igrave;nh mt nh&atilde;n m&aacute;c. Cn c v&agrave;o &oacute; nhn din c &ocirc;i gi&agrave;y c sn xut  &acirc;u? Ng&agrave;y th&aacute;ng sn xut, cht liu, m&agrave;u sc, th trng ph&acirc;n phi, k&iacute;ch thc sn phm&hellip; V&igrave; vy: C&aacute;ch ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c nht  kim tra  tht gi ca mt &ocirc;i gi&agrave;y Nike n &oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; tem gi&agrave;y. Tem gi&agrave;y&nbsp; vi mc &iacute;ch nhm nhn bit v&agrave; bo v sn phm ca m&igrave;nh trc nhng mt h&agrave;ng nh&aacute;i, k&eacute;m cht lng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"giy Nike n\" data-lazy-src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1-34.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"392\" src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1-34.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tem gi&agrave;y Nike thng c &eacute;p nhit hoc may tr&ecirc;n li g&agrave;, m&aacute; trong hoc t&ecirc;n tm l&oacute;t (vi mt s d&ograve;ng nh Flyknit Free Run) ca gi&agrave;y. Tem ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng s c&oacute; nhng c im sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>a. B mt tem b&oacute;ng mn, c&oacute;  co gi&atilde;n nh.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>i vi tem ca gi&agrave;y nike ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng c sn xut h&agrave;ng lot theo mt m&atilde; s kh&aacute;c nhau. Tem c &eacute;p t m&aacute;y nhit, vi mc in l&ecirc;n tem c&oacute;  n&eacute;t cao chu c t&aacute;c ng c&aacute;c yu t h&oacute;a hc v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng phai theo thi gian. B&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i tem c ph mt lp keo b&oacute;ng mn, nhm bo v mc ch tr&ecirc;n tem. Kh&aacute;c vi nhng tem gi d b xung m&agrave;u v&agrave; nh&ograve;a trc nhit  cao v&agrave; nc. i vi tem ca gi&agrave;y nike ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng s kh&ocirc;ng b hai yu t va n&ecirc;u.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>b. M&atilde; sn phm (Check Code):</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>D&atilde;y s c khoanh tr&ograve;n ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; m&atilde; k&yacute; hiu mu v&agrave; m&agrave;u ca gi&agrave;y.  kim tra gi&agrave;y tht hay gi bn ch cn g&otilde; d&ograve;ng m&atilde; n&agrave;y k&egrave;m theo ch &ldquo;Nike&rdquo; tr&ecirc;n trang t&igrave;m kim ri chn phn t&igrave;m kim h&igrave;nh nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"giy Nike n\" data-lazy-src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2-32.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"392\" src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2-32.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>c. Kim tra ph&ocirc;ng ch:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ph&ocirc;ng ch tr&ecirc;n nn tem gi&agrave;y nike l&agrave; ph&ocirc;ng ch c trng d&ugrave;ng  nhn din thng hiu ca Nike k&egrave;m logo m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng mt n v n&agrave;o c&oacute; th l&agrave;m nh&aacute;i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"giy Nike n\" data-lazy-src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/3-30.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"253\" src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/3-30.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ch in m m&agrave;u, sc n&eacute;t, c&oacute; khong c&aacute;ch v&agrave; chiu cao u nhau. C&ograve;n gi&agrave;y gi thng s in ch lem luc v&agrave; ph&ocirc;ng ch cng kh&ocirc;ng thng nht. (nh: etasi.vn)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"giy Nike n\" data-lazy-src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/4-21.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"253\" src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/4-21.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">c bit, c&aacute;c ch &ldquo;e&rdquo; trong d&ograve;ng &ldquo;nikebetterworld.com&rdquo; s c&oacute; phn u&ocirc;i lu&ocirc;n c vut nhn. (nh: etasi.vn)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"giy Nike n\" data-lazy-src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/5-28.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"253\" src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/5-28.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Khong c&aacute;ch gia c&aacute;c ch &ldquo;MADE&rdquo; trong ch &ldquo;MADE IN VIETNAM&rdquo; cng u nhau ch kh&ocirc;ng bin th&agrave;nh &ldquo;MA DE&rdquo;. (nh: etasi.vn)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>d. i vi tem &eacute;p nhit:</strong>&nbsp;s c&oacute;  phng nht nh do c&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; b&ecirc;n trong, vin tem c gia nhit chy n&ecirc;n b&aacute;m d&iacute;nh u v&agrave;o b mt cht liu gi&agrave;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>e. V tr&iacute; k&yacute; t &ldquo;EUR&rdquo; &ldquo;ng n&oacute;c&rdquo;:</strong>&nbsp;Th&ocirc;ng thng,  d&ograve;ng ghi k&iacute;ch c gi&agrave;y, ch &ldquo;US&rdquo; hoc ch &ldquo;EUR&rdquo; s cao hn c&aacute;c ch &ldquo;UK&rdquo; v&agrave; &ldquo;cm&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"giy Nike n\" data-lazy-src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/6-31.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"253\" src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/6-31.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">a s c&aacute;c d&ograve;ng &ldquo;EUR&rdquo; tr&ecirc;n tem gi&agrave;y u cao hn c&aacute;c ch c&ograve;n li. (nh: etasi.vn)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi&ecirc;n khi tr&ecirc;n tem in m&atilde; nh&agrave; m&aacute;y (ph&iacute;a tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng b&ecirc;n phi) l&agrave; &ldquo;VE&rdquo; (Vit Nam), &ldquo;JJ&rdquo; (Indonesia)&hellip; hoc nhng &ocirc;i&nbsp;gi&agrave;y tr em&nbsp;(Kid&rsquo;s) th&igrave; ch &ldquo;US&rdquo; hoc &ldquo;EUR&rdquo; s kh&ocirc;ng c in cao hn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>f. ng thng t l:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bn k mt ng thng t u du &ldquo;Swoosh&rdquo; xung, n&oacute; s i qua gia ch &ldquo;t&rdquo; v&agrave; &ldquo;e&rdquo; ca d&ograve;ng &ldquo;nikebetterworld.com&rdquo;, gia ch &ldquo;U&rdquo; v&agrave; &ldquo;K&rdquo; ca d&ograve;ng &ldquo;UK&rdquo; v&agrave; ch s th 3 tr&ecirc;n d&ograve;ng M&atilde; sn phm.<img alt=\"giy Nike n\" data-lazy-src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/7-27.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"253\" src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/7-27.jpg\" width=\"500\" /><br />\r\nng thng t l tr&ecirc;n gi&agrave;y gi s b lch hn i. (nh: etasi.vn)</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>2. Ph&acirc;n bit gi&agrave;y Nike n ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng qua cht liu v&agrave; cht lng gia c&ocirc;ng</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c sn phm Nike ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng c&oacute; cht liu tt hn rt nhiu so vi gi&agrave;y fake. Vi quy tr&igrave;nh sn xut kh&eacute;p k&iacute;n. Mi b phn ca gi&agrave;y c chun h&oacute;a bi c&aacute;c b phn gia c&ocirc;ng kh&aacute;c nhau. Nh b phn  s do xng  sn xut, b phn d&aacute;n keo s do xng keo ph tr&aacute;ch,&hellip;. Cho n&ecirc;n s cho ra mt &ocirc;i gi&agrave;y chun kh&ocirc;ng b li  c&aacute;c kh&acirc;u d&ugrave; l&agrave; nh nht.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>i vi c&aacute;c sn phm gi&agrave;y nike b li, s c nh&agrave; m&aacute;y thu hi v&agrave; ct b c mt d&acirc;y chuyn ( ch kh&ocirc;ng phi loi b tng &ocirc;i ). N&ecirc;n gi&agrave;y nike ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng s kh&ocirc;ng bao gi b li d&ugrave; l&agrave; yu t nh nht.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"giy Nike n\" data-lazy-src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/8-3.png\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"434\" src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/8-3.png\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>H&igrave;nh nh:&nbsp;gi&agrave;y Nike n</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c  gi&agrave;y ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng &ecirc;m v&agrave; mm hn tuy nhi&ecirc;n form vn rt chc chn v&agrave; ng form kh&ocirc;ng b mt form khi mang mt thi gian l&acirc;u d&agrave;i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phn tr&ecirc;n ca c&aacute;c mu gi&agrave;y real rt tinh t v&agrave; t m trong tng chi tit, c bit l&agrave; vi nhiu mu gi&agrave;y Nike c&oacute; ph&acirc;n th&acirc;n c&oacute; kt cu phc tp nh Nike Flyknit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V cht lng gia c&ocirc;ng th&igrave; vi sn phm gi&agrave;y Nike ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng, cht lng gia c&ocirc;ng cc k&igrave; tinh xo, c bit  c&aacute;c ng may di l&oacute;t gi&agrave;y, c&aacute;c ng may tr&ecirc;n upper di li g&agrave; thng rt u v&agrave; hu nh kh&ocirc;ng b li ch. t bit ti c&aacute;c ng keo, rt gn g&agrave;ng v&agrave; sch. Cho n&ecirc;n nu gi&agrave;y nike ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng p l&agrave; iu m&agrave; c&aacute;c gi&agrave;y nike FAKE kh&aacute;c kh&ocirc;ng th so s&aacute;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"giy Nike n\" data-lazy-src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/9-4.png\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"238\" src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/9-4.png\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>H&igrave;nh nh:&nbsp;gi&agrave;y Nike n</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, ng&agrave;y nay mc  tinh xo ca gi&agrave;y Nike FAKE ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng c ci thin. Nu bn kh&ocirc;ng  &yacute; k s d b nhm ln gia tht v&agrave; gi.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>3. Ph&acirc;n bit gi&agrave;y Nike n ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng qua gi&aacute; b&aacute;n</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti hai th trng ln nht Vit Nam l&agrave; H Ch&iacute; Minh v&agrave; H&agrave; Ni. Nguy&ecirc;n ca lng t kh&oacute;a search tr&ecirc;n google, 2 keyword vn c t&iacute;n  gi&agrave;y nike ch&uacute; &yacute; &oacute; l&agrave; &ldquo;gi&agrave;y nike ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng h ch&iacute; minh&rdquo; v&agrave; &ldquo;gi&agrave;y nike ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng h&agrave; ni&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti hai th trng n&agrave;y, c&aacute;c bn c tip cn nhiu ngun th&ocirc;ng tin t c&aacute;c din &agrave;n, c&aacute;c webstie b&aacute;n gi&agrave;y nike. Nhng vn con ln tn  i t&igrave;m &acirc;u l&agrave; gi&agrave;y nike ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng. Yu t l&agrave;m c&aacute;c bn ln tn &oacute; l&agrave; gi&aacute; b&aacute;n?</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"giy Nike n\" data-lazy-src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/10-22.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"395\" src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/10-22.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>H&igrave;nh nh:&nbsp;gi&agrave;y Nike n</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&oacute; ca h&agrave;ng gi&agrave;y A b&aacute;n nike ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng gi&aacute; 2 triu, nhng cng c&oacute; ca h&agrave;ng gi&agrave;y B b&aacute;n sn phm tng t gi&aacute; 3 triu, hoc c&oacute; ca h&agrave;ng li gi&aacute; thp hn 2 triu. Yu t gi&aacute; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c bn b x&aacute;o trn nhn thc trong vic ph&acirc;n bit &acirc;u l&agrave; tht &acirc;u l&agrave; gi. D&ugrave; &atilde; c k c hai yu t nhn bit gi&agrave;y nike tht vi mc  ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c cao  tr&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>i vi gi&agrave;y nike ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng, gi&aacute; cho mt &ocirc;i gi&agrave;y tht kh&oacute;  thp hn 2 triu. Ch mt s trng hp c b&aacute;n trong s kin Bigsale hoc gi&agrave;y tn kho ca c&aacute;c ca h&agrave;ng gi&agrave;y nike cn c thanh l&yacute;. i vi gi&agrave;y nike FAKE cht lng b&igrave;nh thng c&oacute; gi&aacute; t 300-700 ngh&igrave;n/ &ocirc;i, t&ugrave;y sn phm v&agrave; mu m&atilde;. i vi gi&agrave;y Nike FAKE vi cht lng tt hn&nbsp; gi&aacute; c&oacute; th giao ng tr&ecirc;n di 1 triu. &acirc;y ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; c&aacute;ch m&agrave; c&aacute;c bn i mua d b sp by do ch&iacute;nh bn th&acirc;n m&igrave;nh to n&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&ldquo;Tin n&agrave;o ca y&rdquo; &oacute; l&agrave; c&aacute;i gi&aacute; ca nhng gi&agrave;y hiu m&agrave; bn cn chi ti&ecirc;u. Mc  ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c ca c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y ri v&agrave;o khong 65%.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>4. Ph&acirc;n bit qua m&ugrave;i keo d&aacute;n ca gi&agrave;y Nike n</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Bo i ngi m&ugrave;i keo gi&agrave;y nghe c&oacute; v l bch, nh i mua mt m&oacute;n n phi ngi n&oacute; trc vy. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, do t&iacute;nh c th&ugrave; trong chui sn xut kh&eacute;p k&iacute;n. N&ecirc;n keo  d&aacute;n gi&agrave;y Nike cng kh&aacute;c vi keo ca c&aacute;c loi gi&agrave;y kh&aacute;c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Mt c&acirc;u hi t ra l&agrave; &ldquo; t&ocirc;i cha thy keo &oacute; h&igrave;nh dng th n&agrave;o, m&ugrave;i ra l&agrave;m sao th&igrave; l&agrave;m th n&agrave;o  ph&acirc;n bit c&rdquo;. ng vi, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i &atilde; tng test qua v&agrave; ang chia s li cho c&aacute;c bn sau &acirc;y.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" data-lazy-src=\"https://thatlungnam.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/11-19.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"424\" src=\"https://thatlun