chc chc &ocirc;i gi&agrave;y &oacute; thc s va vi b&agrave;n ch&acirc;n m&igrave;nh. Nu sau mt thi gian m&agrave; ch&acirc;n c&oacute; cm gi&aacute;c au, r&aacute;t th&igrave; ng ngn ngi m&agrave; b qua &ocirc;i &oacute; v&igrave; ch&uacute;ng kh&ocirc;ng d&agrave;nh cho&nbsp; bn &acirc;u. Cng ng v&igrave; qu&aacute; tic m&agrave; tc li mua v ri cui c&ugrave;ng li chng s dng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H&atilde;y d&agrave;nh ra mt hoc hai ting  la chn tht k. ng v&igrave; n&oacute;ng vi m&agrave; chn ba. Bn s mt c ch&igrave; ln ch&agrave;i y!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>3. N&ecirc;n chn mua gi&agrave;y Nike v&agrave;o bui chiu ti</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Th&ecirc;m mt kinh nghim mua gi&agrave;y Nike c &uacute;c kt &oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; n&ecirc;n mua gi&agrave;y v&agrave;o bui chiu ti. Thc cht cng kh&ocirc;ng ri&ecirc;ng g&igrave; gi&agrave;y NIke m&agrave; vi bt k &ocirc;i gi&agrave;y, d&eacute;p n&agrave;o cng th.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau mt ng&agrave;y i li, b&agrave;n ch&acirc;n ca bn s t mc gi&atilde;n n ln nht n&ecirc;n thi im chiu ti s th&iacute;ch hp  bn chn c &ocirc;i gi&agrave;y va ch&acirc;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu mua v&agrave;o bui s&aacute;ng th&igrave; rt c&oacute; th bn s ri v&agrave;o trng hp bui s&aacute;ng va vn bui chiu cht n&iacute;ch. Nh vy bn ang trc tip li hi &ocirc;i ch&acirc;n ca m&igrave;nh y!</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"546\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" src=\"https://kiza.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/http-2F2Fhypebeast.com2Fimage2F20172F012Fnike-air-zoom-pegasus-92-stadium-green-makeover-1.jpg\" srcset=\"https://kiza.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/http-2F2Fhypebeast.com2Fimage2F20172F012Fnike-air-zoom-pegasus-92-stadium-green-makeover-1.jpg 820w, https://kiza.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/http-2F2Fhypebeast.com2Fimage2F20172F012Fnike-air-zoom-pegasus-92-stadium-green-makeover-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://kiza.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/http-2F2Fhypebeast.com2Fimage2F20172F012Fnike-air-zoom-pegasus-92-stadium-green-makeover-1-768x511.jpg 768w\" width=\"820\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mt tip nho nh trong kinh nghim mua gi&agrave;y Nike n&agrave;y l&agrave; h&atilde;y chn size gi&agrave;y rng hn ch&acirc;n bn mt ch&uacute;t  m bo vic i li c thoi m&aacute;i nht nh&eacute;! Ph&ograve;ng trng hp bn i tt qu&aacute; d&agrave;y m&agrave;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>4. Kim tra k cht lng gi&agrave;y</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Hn bn &atilde; tng nghe mi ngi n&oacute;i d&ugrave; mua bt c th g&igrave; cng phi kim tra cht lng tht k &uacute;ng kh&ocirc;ng? ng nhi&ecirc;n vic mua&nbsp;<strong>gi&agrave;y Nike&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;cng kh&ocirc;ng phi ngoi l. Bn kh&ocirc;ng th m bo tuyt i rng &ocirc;i<strong>&nbsp;gi&agrave;y Nike&nbsp;</strong>bn sp mua m bo 100% v ng kim ch, keo d&iacute;nh hay lp l&oacute;t,  gi&agrave;y. C&ocirc;ng vic kim tra gn nh l&agrave; bt buc  tr&aacute;nh trng hp mua v nh&agrave; ri bn mi ph&aacute;t hin ra sai s&oacute;t. Ngo&agrave;i ra h&atilde;y hi k ngi b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng v ch  bo h&agrave;nh  m bo quyn li ca m&igrave;nh nh&eacute;!</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"366\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" src=\"https://kiza.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/giay_nike_chinh_hang_1.jpg\" srcset=\"https://kiza.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/giay_nike_chinh_hang_1.jpg 550w, https://kiza.vn/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/giay_nike_chinh_hang_1-300x200.jpg 300w\" width=\"550\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr&ecirc;n &acirc;y shop&nbsp;&atilde; gi &yacute; gi&uacute;p bn mt v&agrave;i kinh nghim mua gi&agrave;y Nike qu&yacute; b&aacute;u. B&acirc;y gi bn &atilde; c&oacute; th y&ecirc;n t&acirc;m hn trong vic chn mua&nbsp;<strong>gi&agrave;y Nike</strong>&nbsp;ri ch? H&atilde;y &aacute;p dng nhng kinh nghim tr&ecirc;n  t&igrave;m c mt &ocirc;i gi&agrave;y Nike nh &yacute; nh&eacute;! Bn cng c&oacute; th gh&eacute; trc tip Kiza  t&igrave;m nhng mu gi&agrave;y Nike ng &yacute; v&agrave; ang l&agrave; hot trend tr&ecirc;n th trng nh&eacute;!</p>\r\n','2019-06